                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Le nuage a passé : tu renais au bonheur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Comme aux vents printaniers l’herbe se renouvelle ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Tu ris, tu crois encore à la brise infidèle,",
